Mens Sneakers

Athletic shoes. Tennis shoes. Trainers. Whatever you call them, men's sneakers are essentials that belong in every guy's closet. At Macy's, you'll find all kinds of sneakers for men, from the gym shoes you'll wear withworkout clothesto fashion sneakers that'll spiff up yourchinosandpolo shirton the weekend. Here's the intel on how to shop for the best men's sneakers at Macy's.

Build a Sneaker Wardrobe
Let's get this out of the way now. You need more than one pair of sneakers in your closet. Why? Because the same pair of men's tennis shoes won't cut it for both the gym and Casual Friday at the office. First, enhance your wardrobe with classics likewhite sneakers. Men's white sneakers have a sport-inspired aesthetic but look polished enough to wear with casual clothes.Leather sneakersare another must-have. Are you looking for other types of men's casual sneakers to try? Experiment with trainers, retro runners, dad sneakers, or high tops. High tops offer extra ankle support for sports like basketball and look great with jeans once you're off the court.

Buy Brands You Know and Give New Ones a Shot
Macy's carries the best names in the game when it comes to men's athletic shoes. Shop for favorite brands likeadidas sneakers,Nike sneakers, andConverse. All three brands make iconic kicks and debut new designs and fresh color combos all the time. Do you love the cushioned feel of athletic soles but don't love how men's slip-on sneakers look with your clothes? Then check out the brandHey Dude. Hey Dude moccasin sneakers combine classic moccasin uppers with flexible sneaker outsoles for a shoe that's a clever hybrid of both styles.

Shop men's sneakers andmen's shoes, available at Macy's.
